HEADWORD: deviled egg
<hw>deviled egg</hw> <def>a hard-boiled egg, sliced into halves and with
the yolk removed and replaced with a paste, usually made from the yolk
and mayonnaise, seasoned with salt and/or spices such as
paprika.</def>⟦br⟧
